# Day 884

![A VI BE](https://miro.medium.com/1*IUqfQ1x4BqgJzBO0Zum-kA.png)

Picked my boy up from Orlando today. Glad to have him visiting the bang' em. Crushed a 3-mile run non-stop, felt exhausted the whole way but seeing my friend run nonstop made me run nonstop. Post-run, fired up the grill for a proper feast. Steaks, chicken, and onions topped off with way too many cookies and milk for dessert. No regrets though. Capped the night with a killer episode of Kill Tony. Laughed so hard my abs got a second workout. Comedy, sweat, and solid company. Can't beat life's simple pleasures :)
